---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy & Security Policy | Solid Properties">
  <Navbar />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 prose prose-gray">
    <h1>Privacy &amp; Security Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">Solid Properties &amp; Investments LLC is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as when you submit a property address, email, or phone number through our forms. This may include name, contact information, and details about real estate you wish to sell.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide cash offers</li>
      <li>To improve our services and website experience</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard security measures and Cloudflare services to protect your data. All form submissions are protected by Cloudflare Turnstile.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy requests, email us at <a href="mailto:info@solidpropertiesllc.com">info@solidpropertiesllc.com</a> or call 619-777-6088.</p>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Layout>